        "Description": "There have been reports coming from Chongqing of malfunctioning PCs.\rTo fix the problems, the Computer Wizard has been using his hex editor to develop a brand new spell.\rHe needs you to run a beta test to ensure there are no bugs.\rThis updated software sorcery can solve the #1 issue in tech support tickets: human error.\rEnd these users.\r\rTHANK YOU TO V1DEOST FOR THE MAGICAL LOGO ART!\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as magicdave94.",
